Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan wins budget cuts
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wd7r
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Jul 1981
Reagan outsmarts Democrats and wins vote on massive budget cuts. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less